zenfoliodown - download photos from zenfolio
--------------------------------------------

zenfolio is a Perl program that downloads photos from a zenfolio album


Installation
------------

Copy the zenfolio program to a directory of your choice.

You'll need the following modules installed, all available from the CPAN:

LWP::UserAgent
XML::Simple

Usage
-----

./zenfoliodown album

Where 'album' is the numeric portion of the album as describe in a typical
zenfolio URL: http://example.zenfolio.com/p123456789.  In this case the
album would be 123456789.

Storage
-------

zenfoliodown currently stores the photos in a directory named 'album' where
album is the album you told zenfolio to go get.
